This is a coconut shell bowl,

581
00:25:55,640 --> 00:25:57,210
and I painted it myself.

582
00:25:58,040 --> 00:25:58,800
You painted this?

583
00:25:58,800 --> 00:25:59,880
Yes, I did.

584
00:25:59,880 --> 00:26:00,360
Beautiful.

585
00:26:01,720 --> 00:26:02,920
This part...

586
00:26:02,920 --> 00:26:04,170
This is your name,

587
00:26:04,880 --> 00:26:06,020
and here's mine.

588
00:26:07,200 --> 00:26:09,600
And over here, it's like

589
00:26:09,600 --> 00:26:11,720
my feelings for you.

590
00:26:11,720 --> 00:26:13,920
They're very…

591
00:26:13,920 --> 00:26:15,200
vibrant.

592
00:26:15,200 --> 00:26:18,010
Feelings that can't be contained.

593
00:26:21,200 --> 00:26:22,600
I know you like blue,

594
00:26:22,600 --> 00:26:24,400
so I used a lot of blue.

595
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:26,000
To me, you're also

596
00:26:26,000 --> 00:26:27,000
someone radiant.

597
00:26:27,000 --> 00:26:29,280
So I painted many stars,

598
00:26:29,280 --> 00:26:30,580
very bright.

599
00:26:31,480 --> 00:26:33,740
I think seeing this will lift your spirits.

600
00:26:34,560 --> 00:26:36,150
There are lots of hearts here.

601
00:26:37,400 --> 00:26:38,360
I really like it.

602
00:26:39,080 --> 00:26:41,100
On the back, there's a little scale,

603
00:26:41,880 --> 00:26:43,300
and a phrase.

604
00:26:46,240 --> 00:26:47,040
Take a look.

605
00:26:47,040 --> 00:26:48,120
I saw it.

606
00:26:48,120 --> 00:26:49,440
You have to turn it to read.

607
00:26:49,440 --> 00:26:51,120
"This is just our beginning."

608
00:26:51,120 --> 00:26:52,170
I know.

609
00:26:52,580 --> 00:26:56,980
(This is just our beginning.)

610
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:59,240
At that moment, I honestly didn't get it,

611
00:26:59,240 --> 00:27:01,200
because what she meant was

612
00:27:01,200 --> 00:27:03,160
that this was just a beginning.

613
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:04,440
But to me,

614
00:27:04,440 --> 00:27:05,640
could that beginning mean

615
00:27:05,640 --> 00:27:07,720
we could start from here

616
00:27:07,720 --> 00:27:09,080
as a couple?

617
00:27:13,600 --> 00:27:14,480
No matter what,

618
00:27:15,600 --> 00:27:17,280
whether it's a beginning or something else,

619
00:27:18,280 --> 00:27:21,480
I still want a clear answer.

620
00:27:21,480 --> 00:27:23,000
Because

621
00:27:23,000 --> 00:27:24,800
I'm certain about my feelings for you,

622
00:27:24,800 --> 00:27:26,960
and I hope to get that same certainty from you.

623
00:27:28,600 --> 00:27:30,550
Just take ten seconds

624
00:27:32,120 --> 00:27:35,280
to think about everything we've shared here,

625
00:27:35,280 --> 00:27:36,140
and

626
00:27:37,080 --> 00:27:37,840
the feeling

627
00:27:37,840 --> 00:27:40,040
when we're together.

628
00:27:40,040 --> 00:27:40,610
And...

629
00:27:43,200 --> 00:27:44,940
I will respect

630
00:27:45,520 --> 00:27:46,920
any decision

631
00:27:46,920 --> 00:27:48,460
you make, but-

632
00:27:51,880 --> 00:27:53,280
I want to

633
00:27:53,280 --> 00:27:55,800
know your answer.

634
00:27:55,800 --> 00:27:57,640
Here's a lighter.

635
00:27:57,640 --> 00:27:59,030
You have ten seconds.

636
00:28:01,120 --> 00:28:01,880
Answer to what?

637
00:28:03,600 --> 00:28:04,510
If

638
00:28:05,600 --> 00:28:06,120
it's a yes,

639
00:28:06,120 --> 00:28:07,600
light up this sparkler

640
00:28:07,600 --> 00:28:09,370
and tell me you would.

641
00:28:09,370 --> 00:28:10,020
(In ten seconds,)

642
00:28:10,020 --> 00:28:10,720
(if you want to be with me,)

643
00:28:10,720 --> 00:28:11,560
I would what?

644
00:28:11,560 --> 00:28:12,660
(light this sparkler for me,)

645
00:28:12,660 --> 00:28:13,770
(and tell me your answer is yes.)

646
00:28:13,800 --> 00:28:14,730
Want to be with me?

647
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:18,720
You still don't get it, do you?

648
00:28:51,520 --> 00:28:52,570
I like you.

649
00:28:53,320 --> 00:28:53,880
Yes.

650
00:28:53,880 --> 00:28:54,560
I really like you,

651
00:28:54,560 --> 00:28:55,380
especially

652
00:28:55,840 --> 00:28:56,960
when it's just the two of us.

653
00:28:56,960 --> 00:28:58,640
You're the only one in my heart.

654
00:28:58,640 --> 00:29:02,200
You always fill my day with surprises.

655
00:29:02,200 --> 00:29:02,960
That's nice.

656
00:29:02,960 --> 00:29:05,920
Even though we're competing physically,

657
00:29:05,920 --> 00:29:08,740
I'll only make a heart for her.

658
00:29:10,160 --> 00:29:11,120
I actually miss you a lot.

659
00:29:11,120 --> 00:29:12,960
It suddenly hit me.

660
00:29:12,960 --> 00:29:14,040
When I'm not with you,

661
00:29:14,040 --> 00:29:15,440
I can't focus on anything.

662
00:29:15,440 --> 00:29:18,990
♪I truly want to be with you♪

663
00:29:21,680 --> 00:29:23,000
What's going on?

664
00:29:23,000 --> 00:29:24,660
Hold on a sec.

665
00:29:24,700 --> 00:29:26,360
Wait, wait, wait.

666
00:29:27,000 --> 00:29:27,720
I'm lost here.

667
00:29:27,720 --> 00:29:28,200
I think

668
00:29:28,200 --> 00:29:29,800
Jiayi has a lot going on

669
00:29:29,800 --> 00:29:31,040
beneath the surface.

670
00:29:32,120 --> 00:29:32,880
A deep thinker.

671
00:29:32,880 --> 00:29:34,000
She doesn't always show it.

672
00:29:34,000 --> 00:29:35,200
She keeps her thoughts to herself.

673
00:30:10,080 --> 00:30:11,150
So, your answer is no,

674
00:30:12,600 --> 00:30:13,280
right?

675
00:30:16,320 --> 00:30:17,960
I just told you.

676
00:30:17,960 --> 00:30:18,820
Well-

677
00:30:20,760 --> 00:30:21,480
It's okay.

678
00:30:21,480 --> 00:30:23,600
I still have a surprise for you.

679
00:30:34,360 --> 00:30:35,540
That startled me!

680
00:30:36,960 --> 00:30:38,530
Did she say yes?

681
00:30:42,200 --> 00:30:44,050
He got those fireworks for her.

682
00:30:44,380 --> 00:30:45,030
Yeah.

683
00:30:56,510 --> 00:31:00,160
♪If your heart is always searching♪

684
00:31:00,160 --> 00:31:03,240
♪Can you ever find a home♪

685
00:31:03,650 --> 00:31:06,990
♪I've been looking for that someone♪

686
00:31:06,990 --> 00:31:09,430
♪I'll never make it on my own♪

687
00:31:09,430 --> 00:31:15,340
♪Dreams can't take the place of loving you♪

688
00:31:15,510 --> 00:31:18,150
♪In the best way that I can♪

689
00:31:18,150 --> 00:31:24,110
♪I can't take a day without you here♪

690
00:31:24,110 --> 00:31:29,300
♪You are the light that
makes my darkness disappear♪

691
00:31:29,480 --> 00:31:30,560
Lighting this sparkler

692
00:31:30,560 --> 00:31:32,280
means we're officially together.

693
00:31:32,280 --> 00:31:33,130
No.

694
00:31:37,200 --> 00:31:38,880
I just want to light it for you.

695
00:31:40,620 --> 00:31:43,980
♪Knows that it's forever♪

696
00:31:43,980 --> 00:31:46,960
♪I just gotta let you know♪

697
00:31:47,450 --> 00:31:50,630
♪I never wanna let you go♪

698
00:31:50,990 --> 00:31:53,110
♪'Cause when you look me in your eyes♪

699
00:31:53,110 --> 00:31:58,080
♪And tell me that you love me♪

700
00:31:58,490 --> 00:32:01,690
♪Everything's alright♪

701
00:32:01,690 --> 00:32:05,360
♪When you're right here by my side♪

702
00:32:05,360 --> 00:32:08,520
♪When you look me in your eyes♪

703
00:32:10,040 --> 00:32:10,950
So?

704
00:32:14,120 --> 00:32:15,960
Will you be my girlfriend, Jiayi?

705
00:32:15,960 --> 00:32:20,300
(Will you be my girlfriend?)

706
00:32:20,560 --> 00:32:22,000
(Will you be my girlfriend?)
No.

707
00:32:22,000 --> 00:32:22,720
(No.)
Yes?

708
00:32:22,720 --> 00:32:23,800
No.

709
00:32:23,800 --> 00:32:24,680
Yes or no?

710
00:32:24,680 --> 00:32:25,440
No.

711
00:32:25,440 --> 00:32:26,240
Say it again.

712
00:32:26,240 --> 00:32:27,780
I said no.

713
00:32:38,120 --> 00:32:39,200
I'm sure that

714
00:32:39,200 --> 00:32:42,480
we do like each other.

715
00:32:42,480 --> 00:32:43,440
But I don't

716
00:32:43,440 --> 00:32:45,040
want us to rush into this.

717
00:32:45,040 --> 00:32:46,480
I want to keep getting to know him.

718
00:32:46,480 --> 00:32:47,600
Because here on the island,

719
00:32:47,600 --> 00:32:50,600
everything is so perfect. It feels unreal.

720
00:32:50,600 --> 00:32:50,880
But

721
00:32:50,880 --> 00:32:52,000
in real life,

722
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:53,680
love isn't supposed to be like this.

723
00:32:53,680 --> 00:32:55,880
There will be a lot of pressure

724
00:32:55,880 --> 00:32:58,720
and a lot of emotional
ups and downs in real life.

725
00:32:58,720 --> 00:33:00,120
It won't be like it is here,

726
00:33:00,120 --> 00:33:02,080
where we don't have to work,

727
00:33:02,080 --> 00:33:03,880
manage social circles,

728
00:33:03,880 --> 00:33:05,480
think about the future,

729
00:33:05,480 --> 00:33:07,600
or even watch the clock.

730
00:33:07,600 --> 00:33:08,640
I can't just-

731
00:33:08,640 --> 00:33:12,680
because of a perfect setting,

732
00:33:12,680 --> 00:33:15,280
or a dopamine rush,

733
00:33:15,280 --> 00:33:16,600
and all that-

734
00:33:16,600 --> 00:33:17,200
decide

735
00:33:17,200 --> 00:33:19,800
to jump into a romantic relationship.

736
00:33:19,800 --> 00:33:20,880
Because in my mind,

737
00:33:20,880 --> 00:33:21,960
love is

738
00:33:21,960 --> 00:33:24,520
more of

739
00:33:24,520 --> 00:33:26,080
a long-term game.

740
00:33:26,260 --> 00:33:27,800
(Love is a long-term game.)

741
00:33:27,800 --> 00:33:30,440
I think the best part of a relationship

742
00:33:30,440 --> 00:33:32,410
(Interview, Day 1)
is the talking stage.

743
00:33:35,520 --> 00:33:37,720
During this stage,

744
00:33:37,720 --> 00:33:42,320
people give each other more emotional support.

745
00:33:42,320 --> 00:33:43,680
The longer it lasts, the better.

746
00:33:43,680 --> 00:33:46,320
Who wouldn't want happiness to last?

747
00:33:46,320 --> 00:33:48,760
Make it more exciting for me.

748
00:33:48,760 --> 00:33:51,280
If a man is only proactive for a day or two,

749
00:33:51,280 --> 00:33:52,800
even if he seems interested

750
00:33:52,800 --> 00:33:54,920
and I feel a spark,

751
00:33:54,920 --> 00:33:56,960
I still wouldn't let it happen.

752
00:33:56,960 --> 00:33:58,200
What can you really do in one day?

753
00:33:58,200 --> 00:34:00,280
I don't think that proves anything.

754
00:34:00,280 --> 00:34:02,560
I didn't ask you to put in that much effort.

755
00:34:02,560 --> 00:34:03,920
If you're tired, don't do it.

756
00:34:03,920 --> 00:34:04,520
Honestly,

757
00:34:04,520 --> 00:34:05,960
I'm not at the point

758
00:34:05,960 --> 00:34:07,840
where I need to make a choice yet.

759
00:34:07,840 --> 00:34:09,080
Because every day I discover

760
00:34:09,080 --> 00:34:10,400
something new about you.

761
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:11,000
You know what?

762
00:34:11,000 --> 00:34:12,200
You can't do that because a guy...

763
00:34:12,200 --> 00:34:13,080
like...

764
00:34:13,080 --> 00:34:13,440
Doing well?

765
00:34:13,440 --> 00:34:15,080
Maybe he just did some

766
00:34:15,080 --> 00:34:16,080
basic nice things.

767
00:34:16,080 --> 00:34:17,520
Don't mistake that for...

768
00:34:17,520 --> 00:34:18,360
He's a good person?

769
00:34:18,360 --> 00:34:19,480
Mutual love.

770
00:34:19,480 --> 00:34:21,000
Mutual love is far more than

771
00:34:21,000 --> 00:34:22,280
giving each other

772
00:34:22,280 --> 00:34:24,520
a small piece of treat.

773
00:34:24,520 --> 00:34:25,200
What's it like?

774
00:34:25,200 --> 00:34:26,680
It's not like I'd drive hours to see you

775
00:34:26,680 --> 00:34:27,960
and you'd fly hours to see me.

776
00:34:27,960 --> 00:34:30,720
I think true mutual love
is so much more than that.

777
00:34:30,720 --> 00:34:32,680
The early stage of a relationship

778
00:34:32,680 --> 00:34:34,640
should last longer and go deeper.

779
00:34:34,640 --> 00:34:36,880
Extend the talking stage,

780
00:34:36,880 --> 00:34:38,600
but don't just "talk" to him.

781
00:34:38,600 --> 00:34:40,160
Let him enter your life

782
00:34:40,160 --> 00:34:40,800
and help you...

783
00:34:40,800 --> 00:34:41,200
Go deeper.

784
00:34:41,200 --> 00:34:41,960
In my opinion,

785
00:34:41,960 --> 00:34:43,280
love really is

786
00:34:43,280 --> 00:34:45,520
a long-term battle.

787
00:34:45,520 --> 00:34:47,840
Go ahead and flip it upside down.

788
00:34:47,840 --> 00:34:48,680
On Balance Island,

789
00:34:48,680 --> 00:34:50,160
no one can put pressure on me.

790
00:34:50,160 --> 00:34:51,280
I still hope

791
00:34:51,280 --> 00:34:52,520
that

792
00:34:52,520 --> 00:34:55,440
I can truly be with

793
00:34:55,440 --> 00:34:57,520
the person I love

794
00:34:57,520 --> 00:34:58,960
in the real world.

795
00:34:58,960 --> 00:34:59,560
And

796
00:34:59,560 --> 00:35:02,040
I hope the relationship is

797
00:35:02,040 --> 00:35:02,960
solid and stable-

798
00:35:02,960 --> 00:35:05,240
one can face any challenge.

799
00:35:16,480 --> 00:35:17,680
I like her so much

800
00:35:17,680 --> 00:35:20,880
that I went a bit over the top.

801
00:35:20,880 --> 00:35:23,820
I pushed her for a certain response.

802
00:35:51,080 --> 00:35:52,040
Do you like it?

803
00:35:52,040 --> 00:35:52,870
Yes,

804
00:35:54,080 --> 00:35:55,360
but this one is prettier.

805
00:35:55,360 --> 00:35:57,370
So what's your answer?

806
00:36:06,440 --> 00:36:08,130
I just told you.

807
00:36:09,240 --> 00:36:10,320
I have no idea.

808
00:36:10,320 --> 00:36:11,840
Was I just wasting my breath then?

809
00:36:13,400 --> 00:36:14,760
So, where are we now?

810
00:36:32,120 --> 00:36:33,220
At the beginning.

811
00:36:34,920 --> 00:36:37,160
But we need to make it official.

812
00:36:40,280 --> 00:36:41,240
No need,

813
00:36:41,240 --> 00:36:41,980
I'm sorry.

814
00:36:45,440 --> 00:36:46,320
Alright.

815
00:36:46,320 --> 00:36:47,520
Where should we go then?

816
00:36:49,520 --> 00:36:50,210
Let's go.

817
00:36:53,160 --> 00:36:54,320
Where are we going?

818
00:36:55,120 --> 00:36:57,040
How would I know?

819
00:36:57,040 --> 00:36:57,680
Want a hug?

820
00:36:57,680 --> 00:36:59,010
Alright, let's do this.

821
00:37:09,120 --> 00:37:10,530
Let's go.

822
00:37:12,160 --> 00:37:13,400
I have a bad feeling about this.

823
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:13,840
Same here.

824
00:37:13,840 --> 00:37:14,520
Yeah.

825
00:37:14,520 --> 00:37:15,480
Let's head back.

826
00:37:15,480 --> 00:37:16,000
Let's go.

827
00:37:16,000 --> 00:37:16,960
We should head back.

828
00:37:16,960 --> 00:37:18,410
Let's go back to the restaurant.

829
00:37:19,480 --> 00:37:20,760
You've got so many sparklers!

830
00:37:20,760 --> 00:37:22,200
How many did you want me to light?

831
00:37:22,200 --> 00:37:22,680
I didn't know

832
00:37:22,680 --> 00:37:23,950
this was so hard.

833
00:37:24,680 --> 00:37:26,880
See? No chance to light one.

834
00:37:26,880 --> 00:37:29,320
It will. I hope it will.

835
00:37:29,320 --> 00:37:31,440
You just forced it.

836
00:37:40,400 --> 00:37:40,880
Let's go.

837
00:37:47,000 --> 00:37:48,780
Hold on.

838
00:37:51,680 --> 00:37:52,810
I can't walk holding this.

839
00:37:57,320 --> 00:37:59,480
I'm not quite following what you mean.

840
00:37:59,480 --> 00:38:01,760
You could have, but you kept pushing me.

841
00:38:01,760 --> 00:38:02,560
I didn't.

842
00:38:02,560 --> 00:38:04,630
That's not true.

843
00:38:09,080 --> 00:38:10,480
So, what was that?

844
00:38:10,480 --> 00:38:11,880
Was it an open ending?

845
00:38:11,880 --> 00:38:14,080
You didn't get a single word I said.

846
00:38:14,080 --> 00:38:14,920
It's an open ending.

847
00:38:14,920 --> 00:38:16,280
You got nothing out of it.

848
00:38:16,280 --> 00:38:17,150
Is that what you meant?

849
00:38:18,200 --> 00:38:19,000
I don't know.

850
00:38:19,000 --> 00:38:19,720
I don't get you.

851
00:38:19,720 --> 00:38:21,400
I don't get you either.

852
00:38:21,400 --> 00:38:23,520
Didn't you hear what I said?

853
00:38:23,520 --> 00:38:24,360
I did.

854
00:38:24,360 --> 00:38:25,160
Then what exactly

855
00:38:25,160 --> 00:38:27,600
were you trying to say?

856
00:38:27,600 --> 00:38:28,480
I just asked you

857
00:38:28,480 --> 00:38:30,280
"do you want to be with me?"

858
00:38:30,280 --> 00:38:31,680
I'd already said everything.

859
00:38:31,680 --> 00:38:33,750
Why did you ask it again?

860
00:38:35,280 --> 00:38:37,400
I said no, and you pretended not to hear it.

861
00:38:40,800 --> 00:38:43,280
We were all up there waiting for your response.

862
00:38:43,280 --> 00:38:45,080
I didn't get what she meant at first.

863
00:38:45,080 --> 00:38:47,280
You didn't get a single word from me,

864
00:38:47,280 --> 00:38:48,270
did you?

865
00:38:49,600 --> 00:38:50,470
Bestie.

866
00:38:52,080 --> 00:38:52,640
What happened?

867
00:38:52,640 --> 00:38:54,200
- What's wrong?
- Nothing.

868
00:38:56,080 --> 00:38:56,750
So?

869
00:38:59,880 --> 00:39:00,800
Are you a couple now?

870
00:39:01,400 --> 00:39:02,000
