01:06:12,080 --> 01:06:12,560
So scary.

1430
01:06:12,560 --> 01:06:14,000
I can't watch myself talking.

1431
01:06:14,180 --> 01:06:16,260
(Better not say that)

1432
01:06:16,340 --> 01:06:17,460
(Help me)

1433
01:06:17,640 --> 01:06:18,280
I'm heading out.

1434
01:06:18,280 --> 01:06:19,440
(Can't bear to look)

1435
01:06:19,440 --> 01:06:20,480
You can't sit still anymore.

1436
01:06:21,130 --> 01:06:22,200
When are you going to kiss?

1437
01:06:23,360 --> 01:06:24,840
You kissed for two minutes, remember?

1438
01:06:24,840 --> 01:06:26,320
No way.

1439
01:06:26,480 --> 01:06:28,360
See? Still kissing.

1440
01:06:28,600 --> 01:06:29,920
Why this one?

1441
01:06:29,920 --> 01:06:31,880
Hope to see you again.

1442
01:06:31,880 --> 01:06:34,200
Bye bye.

1443
01:06:34,450 --> 01:06:36,280
(Balance Island Special Eventon Fri. 12 PM.)
Welcome to Balance Island.

1444
01:06:36,280 --> 01:06:38,760
Now it's islanders' game time.

1445
01:06:38,890 --> 01:06:39,680
(Can't lose)
Gotta win.

1446
01:06:39,720 --> 01:06:40,480
(Have mercy)
Again.

1447
01:06:40,540 --> 01:06:41,020
(Be humble)

1448
01:06:41,100 --> 01:06:41,540
(Helpless)

1449
01:06:41,620 --> 01:06:42,920
(Button stuck)
This button is tricky.

1450
01:06:42,920 --> 01:06:43,620
It's okay!

1451
01:06:43,620 --> 01:06:44,040
(Time's up)
Done!

1452
01:06:44,040 --> 01:06:44,920
Village chief is exhausted.

1453
01:06:45,040 --> 01:06:46,320
(Admiring)
Rock solid, Guanjie.

1454
01:06:46,640 --> 01:06:47,080
(Insanely smooth)
That fast?

1455
01:06:47,920 --> 01:06:49,080
Zero points.

1456
01:06:49,240 --> 01:06:50,360
Seriously?

1457
01:06:50,440 --> 01:06:51,360
Hurry.

1458
01:06:51,760 --> 01:06:53,360
That's for the hand.

1459
01:06:53,360 --> 01:06:54,200
(Complaining)
Not for a head.

1460
01:06:54,880 --> 01:06:55,880
Put it on wrong.

1461
01:06:56,080 --> 01:06:58,040
(Staying low, legs shaking more)
Stop trembling.

1462
01:07:00,260 --> 01:07:00,860
(Total fail)

1463
01:07:04,080 --> 01:07:04,720
Like this.

1464
01:07:05,120 --> 01:07:05,680
A sheep.

1465
01:07:05,750 --> 01:07:06,560
You two are such a match.

1466
01:07:06,800 --> 01:07:07,560
Really?

1467
01:07:07,640 --> 01:07:08,480
Totally a match.

1468
01:07:08,480 --> 01:07:09,120
How so?
